theorem P2_iff_P3_of_open_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hOpenCl : IsOpen (closure (A : Set X))) :
    Topology.P2 A ↔ Topology.P3 A := by
  constructor
  · intro hP2
    exact Topology.P3_of_P2_and_open_closure (A := A) hP2 hOpenCl
  · intro hP3
    exact Topology.P2_of_P3_and_open_closure (A := A) hP3 hOpenCl

theorem P2_of_P3_and_open_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hP3 : Topology.P3 A) (hOpenCl : IsOpen (closure (A : Set X))) :
    Topology.P2 A := by
  -- First, obtain `P1` from `P3` using the openness of `closure A`.
  have hP1 : Topology.P1 A :=
    Topology.P1_of_P3_and_open_closure (A := A) hP3 hOpenCl
  -- Combine `P1` and `P3` to conclude `P2`.
  exact Topology.P2_of_P1_and_P3 (A := A) ⟨hP1, hP3⟩
